<div class="mw-heading mw-heading2">
<h2 id="Personal">Personal</h2>
<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chris_Blattman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Personal"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
<p>Blattman grew up in <a href="/wiki/Ontario" title="Ontario">Ontario, Canada</a>, in a family of bank managers.<sup id="cite_ref-20" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-20"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>20<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> He is married to Jeannie Annan,<sup id="cite_ref-21" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-21"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>21<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> with whom he has two children.
</p>
